    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Test Checklist\n\n### Opening Settings\n- [ ] Go to **Help > Settings**\n- [ ] Settings panel opens as a modal\n- [ ] All fields show default values\n- [ ] Click Cancel to close without saving\n\n### Kernel Auto-Stop (Layer C)\n1. [ ] Open Settings\n2. [ ] Change \"Auto-stop inactive kernels\" to **After 30 minutes**\n3. [ ] Click **Save** - should see green \"Settings saved!\"\n4. [ ] Open a second notebook in another tab\n5. [ ] Start kernel in both tabs\n6. [ ] Stay on this tab for 30+ minutes\n7. [ ] The other tab should show a pause icon and \"kernel stopped\" tooltip\n8. [ ] Click the other tab - should see \"Kernel was stopped to save memory\" placeholder\n\n### Background/UI Suspension Delays\n1. [ ] Open Settings\n2. [ ] Change \"Background suspension delay\" to **15 seconds**\n3. [ ] Change \"UI suspension delay\" to **60 seconds** (1 minute)\n4. [ ] Save settings\n5. [ ] Open a second tab and switch away\n6. [ ] After ~1 minute the second tab should show a moon icon (UI suspended)\n\n### Line Numbers\n1. [ ] Open Settings\n2. [ ] Uncheck \"Show line numbers\"\n3. [ ] Save settings\n4. [ ] NOTE: This currently requires reopening the notebook to take effect\n\n### Font Size\n1. [ ] Open Settings\n2. [ ] Change font size to **18**\n3. [ ] Save settings\n4. [ ] NOTE: This currently requires reopening the notebook to take effect\n\n### Auto-Save Interval\n1. [ ] Open Settings\n2. [ ] Change \"Auto-save interval\" to **10 seconds**\n3. [ ] Save settings\n4. [ ] Make a change to this notebook (run a cell)\n5. [ ] Wait 10 seconds\n6. [ ] Status bar should show green \"Autosaved at HH:MM:SS\"\n7. [ ] The dirty dot on the tab should disappear\n\n### Persistence\n1. [ ] Change some settings and save\n2. [ ] Close Saturn completely\n3. [ ] Reopen Saturn\n4. [ ] Go to Help > Settings\n5. [ ] All your changed settings should still be there\n\n### Settings File Location\n- Windows: `%APPDATA%\saturn\settings.toml`\n- macOS: `~/Library/Application Support/saturn/settings.toml`\n- Linux: `~/.config/saturn/settings.toml`",
      "metadata": {}
    }
  ]
